This is a simple example plug-in for GIMP. It creates a new text layer with
"Hello, World!" on the current image.

I demonstated this plug-in in my "Extending GIMP with Python" talk at Ljubljana
Python Meetup on 20 September 2018. You can find slides here:

https://www.tablix.org/~avian/blog/articles/talks/extending_gimp_python.pdf
